reviewText: This DVD is the third disc on the Broken, Beat and Scarred single box set with the first disc been the standard single disc, second, the same single with a different tracklist, and third, the DVD of its music video.

I bought all three parts of the single. It looks great in my collection. =))  I also think the song BB&S is one of th best tracks from the Death Magnetic album.

Rock on Metallica!!
